    "IntroductionFluid is a general term encompassing both gases and liquids.",
    "The two fluids we are most familiar with are the atmosphere and water: the atmosphere surrounds the entire Earth, and 70% of the Earth's surface is covered by water.",
    "Since ancient times, water and air, on the one hand, have nurtured life.",
    "On the other hand, it also brings natural disasters such as typhoons, floods and droughts to human beings from time to time.",
